data.description: Check out this cute move in ready home! Natural woodwork in kitchen with bar area, one bedroom on each floor, walk out basement, off street parking on parking pad, newer roof, gutters, siding and new private 6ft wood fence. Two Full baths, one on main floor and in lower level. appliances included. Newer furnace and water heater.  Schedule soon!
